---
// Pitch Global section - El Problema y La Promesa
---
import LiquidEffect from './LiquidEffect.jsx';

<section class="pitch relative py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-black via-gray-900 to-black overflow-hidden">
	<!-- <LiquidEffect client:only="react" /> -->
	<div class="container relative z-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
		<h2 class="section-title text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-center mb-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-purple-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
			El Reto del 2026: De Cartelera a Referente Digital
		</h2>
		<p class="intro-text text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-300 text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-16 leading-relaxed">
			La gente va, ve el partido y se va. El consumo se estanca mientras el balón rueda. Rompe el ciclo con tecnología diseñada para entender el comportamiento humano y la euforia colectiva.
		</p>
		<div class="pitch-cards grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
			<div class="card group bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-900/20 to-purple-900/20 backdrop-blur-sm border border-cyan-500/20 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-cyan-400/50 transition-all duration-500 hover:transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-cyan-500/10">
				<div class="icon text-6xl mb-6 text-cyan-400 group-hover:animate-bounce">⏳</div>
				<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">+300% Retención</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">Dinámicas que convierten a extraños en una sola hinchada.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="card group bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-900/20 to-pink-900/20 backdrop-blur-sm border border-purple-500/20 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-purple-400/50 transition-all duration-500 hover:transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-purple-500/10">
				<div class="icon text-6xl mb-6 text-purple-400 group-hover:animate-bounce">🍔</div>
				<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Aceleración de F&B</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">Activación de compras impulsivas sincronizadas con los picos de emoción.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="card group bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-900/20 to-cyan-900/20 backdrop-blur-sm border border-pink-500/20 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-pink-400/50 transition-all duration-500 hover:transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-pink-500/10">
				<div class="icon text-6xl mb-6 text-pink-400 group-hover:animate-bounce">📊</div>
				<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Captura de Leads</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">Convierte tu ecosistema en un activo digital revendible a marcas patrocinadoras.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.pitch {
		padding: 5rem 0;
		background: #111;
	}

	.container {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 2rem;
	}

	.section-title {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: #fff;
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.intro-text {
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		color: #ccc;
		text-align: center;
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto 3rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.pitch-cards {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.card {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		border-radius: 15px;
		padding: 2rem;
		text-align: center;
		transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
	}

	.card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-10px);
		box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.2);
	}

	.icon {
		font-size: 3rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.card h3 {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: #00ffff;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.card p {
		color: #ccc;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.section-title {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}
		.pitch-cards {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>